{"tid":1736531,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[俾次機會英國] 請求英國收回香港大遊行","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:49:08.000Z","uid":17163,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5f45ade7e4001bbc29aa396734bd6045dd43bc","tid":1736531,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"[俾次機會英國] 請求英國收回香港大遊行<br />\n<br />\n咁多國家𥚃面，最要面，最出師有名既就係英國。而家一國兩制擺明係冇用，上次佢地都話叫我地授權佢地做野。<br />\n<br />\n我知道佢地一直都係口交多過打交，不過我諗我地宜家乜野方法都要一次。<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以今個星期六係全太子/旺角發起一次大遊行，11點出發，3點行完，終點係尖沙咀鐘樓，呢個昔日代表香港最繁榮穩定時代既地標，去show俾英國人睇，我地正式受權佢地做野？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地再唔做野，一來又可以令和理非死左條心，唔好以為會有人打救。二來又可以show俾政府睇，我地係唔會驚架。我地爭取民主既心永遠不死！<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔識整文宣，如果有文宣組睇到，又同意我講既野，可否幫手整d文宣？<br />\n<br />\n(之前冇睇日子出左個星期日，自插)"},{"pid":"f55e02fc5fbdc0b3ae17bf60bee0f2ff799d6f76","tid":1736531,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36eff83cbd3432e4fc502793ce1038735cb5bf80","tid":1736531,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9bbd8a1820440bae5b6f6d4caf7bba22ee80a79","tid":1736531,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d71cedf10c108368a992dcf9b136bec9f5cdd3b","tid":1736531,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeddcdb017ac5780d33e5bcd939912831522b1ad","tid":1736531,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜晚無人㗎"},{"pid":"84d36ca653fa3bb510fe268a531d5b767d6d95b0","tid":1736531,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"英國你都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b1c04444ce54164ef4523bef44ff97926db694","tid":1736531,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:17:20.000Z","msg":"唔想佢收回，英國太垃圾，關鍵時刻完全棄港人於不顧<br />\n有人認同想搞無所謂，各有各做，只係個人對英國真係無任何寄望，綏靖政策到而家"},{"pid":"f62dbdc3082ce83a149239ad5e28163508c1ac06","tid":1736531,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"算吧啦 英國"},{"pid":"9bbdd0825ef4fc4846a453f86a8053c75baef86d","tid":1736531,"uid":260796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"照做左先啦<br />\n美國𣄃本來大家都以為冇用㗎<br />\n做完都好大迴響"},{"pid":"10586357513b9e3498d966b2a292f3b9577383f2","tid":1736531,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"搞條命咩大佬<br />\n依家一聚人就等圍捕<br />\n返去狗屋坐水凳定等雞姦<br />\n用條命黎搞聚會遊行？<br />\n<br />\n等知和理非仲有好多<br />\n要轉做勇武先有得打落去<br />\n但呢個方法唔work <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家係要小隊地下化啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"105667b2d95373f757bfd5cb0626b0ceb4e2ab7f","tid":1736531,"uid":12607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"去英領搞集會?"},{"pid":"b0c1c842aba1d5d0f3bbb570989fdb27cd84d6ef","tid":1736531,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105667b2d95373f757bfd5cb0626b0ceb4e2ab7f","tid":1736531,"uid":12607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"去英領搞集會?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}